Package: perpsnip
Type: Package
Title: 'tidymodels' Interface for 'PerpetualBooster'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Joshua", "Marie",
      email = "joshua.marie.k@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides a 'parsnip' model specification for the 'PerpetualBooster'
    algorithm implemented in the 'perpetual' package. PerpetualBooster is a
    self-generalizing gradient boosting machine that eliminates the need for
    hyperparameter search by automatically tuning itself within a user-supplied
    computational budget. This package exposes classification, regression, and
    (optionally) censored regression modes so that PerpetualBooster can be used
    inside any 'tidymodels' workflow, including hyperparameter tuning with
    'tune' and performance evaluation with 'yardstick'.
